The EDS analysis of the 15x(Ti/Zr) /Si multilayer system was performed in order to compare the differences in the elemental composition of unmodified multilayer thin film and the ablated steps for the spot made at the average pulse energy of 17μJ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
